<LP>
   WASHINGTON -- The following issues were recently filed
with the Securities and Exchange Commission:
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   Kimmins Environmental Services Corp., proposed offering of
800,000 common shares, via Whale Securities Co.
                                                                                                       

