<LP>
   Thomasville Furniture Industries Inc., a unit of Armstrong
World Industries, Inc., said it signed a letter of intent to
buy a furniture manufacturing plant in High Point, N.C., from
Ladd Furniture Inc. The amount wasn't disclosed.
