Report:
                                                                                                       

                        CORPORATE
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   Coca-Cola Enterprises Inc. -- $250 million of 8.35% notes
due June 20, 1995 priced at 97.351 to yield 9.02%. The
noncallable notes were priced at a spread of 67 basis points
above the Treasury's five-year note. Rated single-A-2 by
