   Wilmington Trust Co. said it agreed to acquire Sussex
Trust Co. for $68 million, or $42.50 a share, in a tax-free
stock swap.
   Sussex Trust stockholders will receive between 1.037 and
1.149 shares of Wilmington Trust stock for each share of
